Class Snail

  • java.lang.Object
    • Snail
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Snail>

    class Snail
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Snail>
    Class Snail. A snail object has attribute integer type speedSnail and radius snail, String container type imageSnail to save the image paths, and String type image as the curent image path. A snail object is a creature summoned on the bottom of the aquarium.
    Version:
    22 April 2018
    Author:
    Rabbi Fijar Mayoza --13516081
